{\bf\large 114neV aBayx udAharaNe.}
\end{center}

\begin{enumerate}[\rm (1)]
\item Adi pada $\tfrac{1}{2}, 1, 3,$ guNoVtatxra $\tfrac{1}{2}, \tfrac{1}{4}, 4,$ matutx gaCaCxvu $24, 10, 12$ Agalu parxteyxVka aMtayx padagaLeSuTx?

\item obabx arasu modalu divasa $4$ peY, $2$neV divasa $16$ peY, mUraneV divasa $64$ peY I parxkArakekx $16$ divasa dharamxvanunx mADalAgi kaDeV divasa eSuTx vecacxvAga bahudu?
\end{enumerate}
